snippet.title: Consider
snippet.description:
What's up guys! My name is Consider and I post a variety of gaming related content ranging from Autopolitan, an Automation and BeamNG crossover series, to Planet Coaster, Sims, and My Summer Car. Enjoy!! 

 

-----------------------------------------------------
Equipment: (for those interested)

-Recording-
Recording Software: OBS with Audacity
Mic: Blue Baby Bottle (w/ Scarlett 8i6)
Editing Software: Adobe Premiere Pro

-Computer-
Graphics Card: RTX 3090
Processor: AMD Ryzen 9 3900xt 
Motherboard: ROG X570-F
Ram: 32GB
Headphones: Beyerdynamic DT770 Pro
